trans-unit.source: Represents syndication content that consists of a URL to another resource.
trans-unit.target: Representa o conteúdo de sindicalização composto de uma URL para outro recurso.

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates how to use the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent> class.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir demonstra como usar o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent> classe.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" /> class with the specified <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" /> com a instância <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" /> especificada.

trans-unit.source: The media type of the resource referenced by the <see cref="T:System.Uri" />.
trans-unit.target: O tipo de mídia do recurso referenciado pelo <see cref="T:System.Uri" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" /> class with the specified <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> and media type.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" /> com o <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> especificado e o tipo de mídia.

trans-unit.source: The media type parameter can be set to any known MIME type value as defined in [RFC 2046](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=95720).
trans-unit.target: O parâmetro de tipo de mídia pode ser definido para qualquer valor de tipo MIME conhecido, conforme definido em [RFC 2046](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=95720).

trans-unit.source: The following example demonstrates how to call this constructor.
trans-unit.target: O exemplo a seguir demonstra como chamar este construtor.

trans-unit.source: Creates a copy of the existing <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" /> instance.
trans-unit.target: Cria uma cópia da instância de <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" /> existente.

trans-unit.source: A new <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.SyndicationContent" /> instance that contains the new copy of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" />.
trans-unit.target: Uma nova instância <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.SyndicationContent" /> que contém a nova cópia do <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" />.

trans-unit.source: Gets the content type of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtém o tipo de conteúdo do <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" />.

trans-unit.source: The content type can be set to any known MIME type value as defined in [RFC 2046](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=95720).
trans-unit.target: O tipo de conteúdo pode ser configurado para qualquer valor de tipo MIME conhecido, conforme definido em [RFC 2046](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=95720).

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> instance that contains the URI for the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" />.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Uri" /> instância que contém o URI para o <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" />.
O <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlWriter" /> no qual ocorrerá a gravação.

trans-unit.source: Writes the contents of the <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" /> instance to the specified <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlWriter" />.
trans-unit.target: Grava os conteúdos da instância <see cref="T:System.ServiceModel.Syndication.UrlSyndicationContent" /> no <see cref="T:System.Xml.XmlWriter" /> especificado.
